@startuml
title Registrar Medicamento

actor Administrador
participant "UI" as UI
participant "MedicamentoController" as MC
participant "MedicamentoService" as MS
database "DB" as DB

Administrador -> UI : Ingresa datos medicamento
UI -> MC : POST /medicamentos
MC -> MS : guardarMedicamento(dto)
MS -> DB : INSERT Medicamento
DB --> MS : OK
MS --> MC : Confirmación
MC --> UI : Éxito
UI --> Administrador : Medicamento registrado
@enduml
